---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroBanner from "../images/main1.avif";
---

<section class="hero" id="hero">
	<div class="hero-content">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h1>Brisez les chaînes de votre prison mentale</h1>
			<p class="quote">
				"<strong>Le voyage de mille lieues commence par un pas. – Lao Tseu </strong>
			</p>
			<p class="section-subtitle">
				Revenir à soi, c'est <strong>éveiller</strong> votre <strong>force intérieure</strong> et <strong>puiser</strong> dans vos <strong>ressources profondes</strong> pour <strong>briser</strong> les <strong>schémas toxiques</strong>, <strong>surmonter</strong> le <strong>burn-out</strong> et <strong>libérer</strong> votre esprit grâce à l'hypnose. Même lorsque le chemin semble long et difficile, chaque petit pas vous rapproche de la <strong>transformation</strong>. Vous portez en vous tout le <strong>potentiel</strong> nécessaire pour <strong>réécrire</strong> votre histoire.
			</p>
			<p class="hero-description">
				<strong>Reprenez le pouvoir sur votre vie.</strong> À travers la PNL et l'hypnose, je vous accompagne sur le chemin de la <strong>liberté</strong>, pour vous <strong>reconnecter</strong> à votre <strong>essence profonde</strong>.
			</p>
			<a href="https://essence-conscience-decouverte.youcanbook.me" class="cta-btn"
				><strong>Le changement commence ici</strong>.</a
			>
		</div>
	</div>
	<Image
		src={heroBanner}
		alt="Illustration Hero"
		class="hero-img"
		height={2280}
		width={1574}
		decoding="async"
		loading="lazy"
	/>

	<style lang="scss">
		.hero {
			position: relative;
			min-height: 90vh;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			overflow: hidden;

			.hero-content {
				position: relative;
				z-index: 2;
				width: 100%;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 40px;
				text-align: center;
				text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;

				&::before {
					content: "";
					position: absolute;
					top: 50%;
					left: 50%;
					width: 130%;
					height: 150%;
					transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
					background: radial-gradient(
						circle,
						rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0%,
						rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 70%
					);
					z-index: -1;
				}
			}

			.section-header {
				margin-bottom: 30px;

				h1 {
					color: $text-white;
					font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw + 1rem, 4rem);
					margin-bottom: 25px;
					font-weight: 800;
					line-height: 1.1;
					position: relative;
					display: inline-block;
					text-shadow:
						2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
						0 0 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
					letter-spacing: -0.02em;
					animation: slideDown 0.8s ease-out;

					&:after {
						content: "";
						position: absolute;
						bottom: -12px;
						left: 50%;
						transform: translateX(-50%);
						width: 120px;
						height: 4px;
						background: linear-gradient(
							90deg,
							rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 0%,
							rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 50%,
							rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 100%
						);
						border-radius: 2px;
						animation: expandWidth 1s ease-out;
					}
				}

				.section-subtitle {
					font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw + 0.5rem, 1.5rem);
					max-width: 800px;
					margin: 35px auto;
					color: $text-white;
					text-align: justify;
					line-height: 1.6;
					text-shadow:
						1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
						0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
					font-weight: 500;
					animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
				}
			}

			.quote {
				font-style: italic;
				font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw + 0.5rem, 1.4rem);
				color: darken($text-white, 5%);
				margin: 25px 0;
				font-weight: 500;
				opacity: 0.95;
				text-shadow:
					1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
					0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
			}

			.hero-description {
				font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw + 0.5rem, 1.5rem);
				line-height: 1.7;
				margin: 0 auto 45px;
				color: $text-white;
				max-width: 800px;
				font-weight: 500;
				text-align: center;
				text-shadow:
					1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
					0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.9s both;
			}

			.cta-btn {
				display: inline-block;
				background-color: $secondary-color;
				color: white;
				padding: clamp(15px, 2vw + 5px, 20px) clamp(30px, 4vw + 10px, 48px);
				margin-top: clamp(30px, 5vw + 10px, 60px);
				border-radius: 30px;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
				align-self: center;
				text-align: center;
				position: relative;
				z-index: 1;
				letter-spacing: 0.5px;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba($secondary-color, 0.2);

				&:hover {
					transform: translateY(-3px);
					box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba($primary-color, 0.3);
					background: linear-gradient(135deg, $secondary-color, $primary-color);
					background-color: $primary-color;
				}
			}

			.hero-img {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
				z-index: 1;
				opacity: 0.7;
				animation: zoomIn 20s ease-out infinite alternate;
			}

			&::before {
				content: "";
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				background: linear-gradient(
					180deg,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 0%,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 25%,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 75%,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 100%
				);
				z-index: 1;
			}

			// Add a top gradient for better text contrast at the top
			&::after {
				content: "";
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 30vh;
				background: linear-gradient(
					to bottom,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6) 0%,
					rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%
				);
				z-index: 1;
			}
		}

		@keyframes fadeIn {
			from {
				opacity: 0;
				transform: translateY(20px);
			}
			to {
				opacity: 1;
				transform: translateY(0);
			}
		}

		@keyframes slideDown {
			from {
				opacity: 0;
				transform: translateY(-30px);
			}
			to {
				opacity: 1;
				transform: translateY(0);
			}
		}

		@keyframes expandWidth {
			from {
				width: 0;
			}
			to {
				width: 120px;
			}
		}

		@keyframes zoomIn {
			from {
				transform: scale(1);
			}
			to {
				transform: scale(1.1);
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: $mobile) {
			.hero {
				height: 100%;
				min-height: 100vh;

				.hero-content {
					padding: 25px;
					margin: 0 15px;
				}
			}
		}
	</style>
</section>
